---
title: Bruschetta Turkey Salad with Garlic Croutons and Parmesan
description: We've taken the classic Italian antipasto and made it a delicious meal for the whole family! Croutons are pan-fried with garlic oil, then tossed with arugula, juicy tomatoes and fresh basil, and topped with creamy Parmesan.  A final drizzle of balsamic glaze and you're all set!
